  html += '<div class="urgent-flag"><h4>1. HIGH IMPACT \u2014 Sticky Add-to-Cart Bar on Product Pages</h4>';
  html += '<p>On mobile (which likely represents 65\u201375% of your traffic), customers scroll past the main ATC button and lose access to it. A sticky floating ATC bar that remains visible at the bottom of the screen while scrolling drives 5\u201312% mobile conversion lift on average. This is one of the highest-ROI CRO changes for a Shopify product page. Can be implemented via a free or low-cost Shopify app (Sticky Add To Cart Booster, Hextom). Test on the HangSmart TV product page first.</p></div>';

  html += '<div class="urgent-flag"><h4>2. HIGH IMPACT \u2014 Above-the-Fold Video on Product Page Hero</h4>';
  html += '<p>The #1 question your customer has before buying is: \u201cdoes this actually work on my wall?\u201d A 15\u201330 second autoplay (muted) installation video directly in the product image gallery \u2014 as the first or second media item \u2014 answers that question before they even scroll. You already have installation UGC content from Meta ads. The Winning Video (2.00x ROAS) and Animation English Voice MOF (5.77x ROAS) are your two best creatives \u2014 one or both belongs in the product page hero. This alone can lift CVR by 0.3\u20130.8 points.</p></div>';

  html += '<div class="anomaly-box warning"><h4>3. HIGH IMPACT \u2014 Review Volume & Recency on Product Page</h4>';
